title: Zeity Jackson 12/10: Ellen, Northern Lights, Diane Feinstein, Cyberpunk 2077 (last time we promise)
itunes:title: Zeity Jackson 12/10: Ellen, Northern Lights, Diane Feinstein, Cyberpunk 2077 (last time we promise)
description:
On this edition of Zeity Jackson Miles and DJ Danl discuss Ellen Degeneres catching COVID, the Norther Lights appearing in the US, Diane Feinstein being less and less able to do her job, and Danl's early reactions to Cyberpunk 2077.
